OL,5, School caterers could be forced to     
OL,6, serve smaller portions or use cheaper  
OL,7, ingredients due to rising prices, a    
OL,8, major food wholesaler has warned.      
OL,10,FAndrew Selley, boss of Bidfood, said   
OL,11,Fcaterers would face "difficult         
OL,12,Fdecisions" as inflation soars.         
OL,14,FThe warning comes after Bank of England
OL,15,Fgovernor Andrew Bailey said food price 
OL,16,Frises were a "major worry".            
OL,18,FHowever, Marks & Spencer chairman said 
OL,19,Fhe expected the sharp rate at which    
OL,20,Fprices were rising to be temporary.    
